t now), Epic allows for up to 80 characters per line.  However, CDR only allows for 70 characters and chops off any more than that.  So, last week, Rohit had me change the Profile Variable OBX5_MAXLENGTH from 82 to 70 on AIP 898100 in WITSCA, to see if the interface would move the extra characters to the next line (next OBX segment).  However, the HL7 msg was never fully created and the interface event daemon crashed.  So, I changed the PV back to 82.  Need to work further with Sarat and Lisa on this defect, since it might still require an interface change.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Ad hoc installed in Prod on 5/26/06',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-08-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2006-05-26 00:00:00','2006-05-26 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(463,1,45,NULL,40,13,NULL,NULL,NULL,'OP','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'M',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Tx Edit Functionality - Bridges Changes','Lisa Pfeifer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-08-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(464,1,45,NULL,40,13,310,NULL,'C','OP','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N','D','M',NULL,NULL,834645,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Tx Edit Functionality - Bridges Configurations','Lisa Pfeifer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Ani V','KP NCAL wishes to be able to edit transcriptions that arrive over the KP NCAL TRANSCRIPTION - IN interface (898101.) To allow this, table 101 needs to be updated to allow editing from the in basket. \r\nUpdate table 101 to reflect the following:\r\n\r\nTranscription type/Category value     EDITABLE\r\nD - 4                                                               1-YES\r\nH - 28                                                             1-YES\r\nY - 22                                                             1-YES\r\nX - 23                                                              1-YES\r\nC - 25                                                             1-YES\r\nZ - 26                                                              1-YES\r\nB - 24                                                             1-YES\r\nO - 27                                                             1-YES','I have listed all the Bridges Transcription changes currently in the WITS test environment to support edit functionality.  The Transcription interfaces are CDR Tx to Epic (AIP 898101) and Epic Tx to CDR (AIP 898100).  Please note that other changes are being made in the EpicCare application to support this effort.\r\n\r\nTo support edit functionality in Epic for certain transcription types, update table 101 (TRANSCRIPTION DEFINITION TABLE) to reflect the following:\r\n\r\nTranscription type/Category value         EDITABLE\r\nD - 4                                                                   1-YES\r\nH - 28                                                                 1-YES\r\nY - 22                                                                 1-YES\r\nX - 23                                                                  1-YES\r\nC - 25                                                                  1-YES\r\nZ - 26                                                                  1-YES\r\nB - 24                         ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Configurations made in RENCCAM and RENCNBM and WITSCA, WITSGG and WITSCC','RA 310 - Installed in Prod on 5/26/06',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-08-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2006-05-26 00:00:00','2006-05-26 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(465,1,23,NULL,40,13,320,NULL,'C','OP','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N','D','L',NULL,NULL,1075102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lab, CoPath and Rad Results Support UCI for Encounter Matching in SU\'05','Lisa Pfeifer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Aaron M','8/23/06 - RW - Installed in Prod on 8/19/06\r\n8/16/06 - RW - No change\r\n8/8/06 - RW - Will be part of CPOE go-live\r\n7/12/06 - RW - Da